WEBVTT

00:04:58.999 --> 00:05:00.483
well, we can change it.

00:05:01.681 --> 00:05:04.335
How we die is indeed
something we can affect.

00:05:06.446 --> 00:05:10.499
Making the system sensitive
to this fundamental distinction

00:05:10.523 --> 00:05:13.975
between necessary
and unnecessary suffering

00:05:13.999 --> 00:05:17.689
gives us our first of three
design cues for the day.

00:05:18.299 --> 00:05:22.828
After all, our role as caregivers,
as people who care,

00:05:22.852 --> 00:05:27.514
is to relieve suffering --
not add to the pile.